Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:14.74,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:21.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:28.25,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.21,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.46,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
